{"tid":1467890,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[投票] 其實有幾多人係覺得用和平手段可以贏到場革命？","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:40:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T09:21:10.000Z","uid":164420,"like":17,"dislike":92,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"ec6ab9712baf0fb6a88a5ce8c028d54da6ecfee8","tid":1467890,"uid":164420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:40:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />和理非可以取得最終勝利<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />革命必須流血<br />\n<br />\n頭盔，非分化撚，只係想知一眾連登手足既諗法。<br />\n<br />\n因為我開始有d唔明而家香港人到底期望緊d乜？<br />\n<br />\n歴史話你知沒有一場成功既革命係可以用理性和平既方式推翻一個政權。<br />\n<br />\n香港人係咪覺得可以打破歴史？<br />\n<br />\n我唔明，真係唔明<br />\n<br />\n721 811大家都咬牙切齒話要血債血贘，但過一排又話要和理非爭取最大公約數。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n劇本不停loop，大家有冇同樣既感覺？"},{"pid":"7fcb7885ed49e794f3fa44e09353743d7078d4e5","tid":1467890,"uid":68628,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:43:25.000Z","msg":"我淨係知依場運動到而家為止<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">只有示威者不斷流血</span>"},{"pid":"601c97c4694ff5b75c117598c8cebdb5accea8f7","tid":1467890,"uid":164420,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:44:31.000Z","msg":"我自己先負皮自己，我係覺得而家我地面對既對手係一個冇人性既政權，唔覺得佢會講道理"},{"pid":"80fc0cdc5b0bfa3becf1395d89025a9b7d82460a","tid":1467890,"uid":164420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:45:37.000Z","msg":"迷茫推"},{"pid":"c3a5598b73e52e13b6e537491d151836d86e0af4","tid":1467890,"uid":164420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:45:47.000Z","msg":"迷茫推"},{"pid":"2aeab69a9eff01485dbf978db9b92dd841aec593","tid":1467890,"uid":164420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:46:08.000Z","msg":"迷茫推"},{"pid":"7343dc3744e771030f5bb6b74a0b54a555f5189f","tid":1467890,"uid":52574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:46:53.000Z","msg":"從來都唔係【癱唔癱】既問題，而係【如何癱】既問題<br />\n<a href=\"https: